      "span_text": "The original driving force to use quantum dot comes from the expectation for quantum dot to generate multiple excitons upon absorbing a single photon. This would possibly boost the energy conversion efficiency beyond the traditional Shockley and Queisser limit for silicon solar cells [CITATION_1] ."
